{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_020.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1a1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, welcome! I've been waiting for you to come by!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, this is a tavern, right?<CR>Are you sure I'm allowed to come in?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "No, no, no, hold on there, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "As you can see, this is a place to drink, as well as a place to eat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "My aim is for this tavern to be a place where anyone, from lousy men to cute girls, can come freely."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "So there's no need to hold back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see, so that's why the interior is round and kinda cute..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, I did my best to make sure that girls would say this place is cute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'm the owner, as well as the cook, and the bartender, Kyle!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Wow, it's amazing to be so young and have your own shop..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I've worked diligently at a lot of places to save up enough money to open this place up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Although, I repeatedly got fired for talking to girls while I was working!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see. Ah-haha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "(I-I wonder if I should feel bad for<CR>him...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But, I've said good-bye to my days of youth. I'm serious about my job now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Even people who can't drink alcohol, especially the guys who can't drink, come to my tavern!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I have good food and cute sweets, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Now that you mention it, something smells really delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I'm preparing my daily special.<CR>My cooking is really great!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(Whoa! My stomach just rumbled!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Umm...did you hear that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Ha! A loud stomach is proof that your body is healthy. Come on and eat something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I guess I will. What do you have on your menu?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Well, you know...ultimate dishes that use only the highest quality ingredients that only rich people can afford..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Won't be found on my menu, so don't worry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I-I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "But, I do put all my skills into whatever I cook. I hand-pick the ingredients, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "My motto is to provide yummy food at cheap prices."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Kyle, your motto sounds very lovely. It helps me a lot!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Kyle... Hmm...that doesn't really strike me well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... Call me \"Mix Master.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xaa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Doesn't that sound cooler? I've always wanted to be called a \"Master.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Haha, okay, I'll call you Mix Master from now on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "All right! Then I'll go get your food ready for ya!"
        }
    ]
}